•HOW TO SPECIFY THE LANGUAGE OF A PAGE IN HTML5•<!--Add this before your head tag-->
<html lang="en">

•SIGNIFYING THAT YOU ARE USING AN EXTERNAL STYLESHEET FOR CSS•
<link href=”sample.css” type=”text/css” rel=”stylesheet><!--Added within the head tag-->

•SIGNIFYING THAT YOU ARE USING AN INTERNAL STYLESHEET FOR CSS•
<style type=”text/css”>CSS coding goes here….</style><!--Added within the head tag-->

•SIGNIFYING THAT YOU ARE USING INLINE CSS•
<h1 style=”color:#ff0000”>Heading1</h1><!--Inline styling is just basically adding the word 'style' to your html tag and the CSS properties to it-->
<h1 style=”color:#ff0000;margin:5px”>Heading1</h1>

•HOW TO CREATE A LINK•
<a href="https://github.com/SDesires/Random-Code-Snippets">Random-Code-Snippets</a><!--Link to an outside page-->
<a href="mailto:yourmailid@mail.com">Your email address</a><!--link to your email-->

TARGET ATTRIBUTES FOR LINKS
target="blank"<!opens the link up in a new browser page-->
target="top"<!--goes to the top of the page-->
target="bottom"<!--goes to the bottom of the page-->
<!--example of target placement in the code--><a href="https://github.com/SDesires/Random-Code-Snippets" target="blank">Random-Code-Snippets</a>



